ApplyDelta(Vector3, Vector3)

Applies a position and rotation change based on Vector3 values. Position deltas are sent as shorts with 0.1 unit precision, allowing ±3276.7 units per tick. Rotation deltas are sent as shorts with 0.01 degree precision, allowing ±327.67 degrees per tick.
